# Cloop - AI-Powered Educational Platform

Cloop is a comprehensive educational platform featuring an AI tutor that provides personalized learning experiences. The platform consists of a React Native frontend built with Expo and a Node.js backend with PostgreSQL database.

## ğŸš€ Project Overview

Cloop aims to provide students with an intelligent tutoring system that adapts to their learning style, grade level, and educational board requirements. The platform offers both structured topic-based learning and general chat functionality.

